---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about TrustMeBro - the Gen Z news platform that makes boring news actually interesting.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="min-h-screen pt-8 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">
          <span class="gradient-text">About</span> TrustMeBro
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">the news site that actually slaps 🔥</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">Our Mission 🎯</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Let's be real - traditional news is boring. Like, genuinely sleep-inducing. 
            We started TrustMeBro because we believe staying informed shouldn't feel like homework.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We take real news from trusted sources and rewrite it in a way that actually makes sense 
            to people who grew up on the internet. No cap, just facts - served with a side of humor.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">How It Works 🤖</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-3">📰</div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">We Gather News</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">From legit sources like Reuters, AP, TechCrunch, and more</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🤖</div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">AI Rewrites It</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Our AI makes it entertaining while keeping facts accurate</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🔥</div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">You Stay Informed</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Without wanting to fall asleep. Revolutionary, we know.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- AI Disclosure -->
          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">📋 AI Disclosure</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <strong>Transparency matters to us.</strong> Articles on TrustMeBro are written with AI assistance. 
              We use large language models to rewrite news from verified sources in an engaging, accessible style. 
              The original facts and reporting come from established news outlets — we link to sources when available. 
              Our team reviews content for accuracy, but we encourage readers to verify important information 
              from primary sources.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">Our Values 💜</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-xl">✅</span>
              <span><strong>Facts First:</strong> We never make stuff up. All news is from verified sources.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-xl">😂</span>
              <span><strong>Entertainment:</strong> News should be engaging, not a snooze-fest.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-xl">🌍</span>
              <span><strong>Accessible:</strong> No jargon, no gatekeeping. Just the tea.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-xl">⚡</span>
              <span><strong>Fast:</strong> Breaking news, but make it digestible.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">The Team 👥</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We're a small team of chronically online individuals who wanted to make news better. 
            Our AI bot does the heavy lifting, but humans make sure everything stays accurate and on point.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
            Got feedback? We'd love to hear from you → <a href="/contact" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Contact Us</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
